===Etymology===
Coined by French [[Marxist]] philosopher [[w:Louis Althousser|Louis Althousser]]

===Noun===
[[Category:English nouns]]
'''interpellation'''

#The act of [[interpel]]ling or [[interrupt]]ing; [[interruption]].
#The act of [[interpose|interposing]] or [[intercede|interceding]]; [[intercession]].
#An act of [[interpel]]lating, or of [[demand]]ing of an officer an [[explanation]] of his action; imperative or peremptory questioning; a point raised in a debate.
#An official [[summons]] or [[citation]].

